{"tid":1325751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[大灣區]有冇辦法要班投共官員/議員/兇殘警 生生世世困係大灣區","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T09:49:55.000Z","uid":229916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a071a7fccf8bd762721d323116dd2ff38dd7a39a","tid":1325751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:36:41.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知港人最愛旅遊<br />\n日韓星馬泰台<br />\n年年成堆港人去<br />\n<br />\n但是班投共官員/議員/黑警，一邊享受住自由社會帶來的民主自由，但是一邊就為左錢投共破壞民主自由的基石。<br />\n<br />\n有冇方法向一d 民主國家禁止呢d 官員入境/入境要特別審批<br />\n<br />\n我知道未有美國人權法下係比較難，但可唔可以由淺入深，由台灣做起，台灣之後到日本，之後泰國等等<br />\n<br />\n可能最後冇用，但是付出少少人力物力，冇後果點解唔做。<br />\n<br />\n如果有人肯帶頭做，我願意幫手同捐錢"},{"pid":"a3afd3b688e09ae3484a70bbfcb7781512d74e9b","tid":1325751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"721 721 721"},{"pid":"68ec800b221b7d0a8316e55e5a8878a8293b2e7d","tid":1325751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"cf80971dd6e552610c6295cf67b41fb7ea2bef22","tid":1325751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6691d6fd52338039368cba17c10d64c632ebdd1d","tid":1325751,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"ace627c30188f480a315f9ae3366f15213c2d3e3","tid":1325751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"9cc62624dba4b38728550dd5aac16fd361da8773","tid":1325751,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"5ae0e6aaff060bc5fff3de43037e219f5bb13dd9","tid":1325751,"uid":165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"721"}]}